the kudzu drink they serve at this inn is super delicious!

37
00:03:19,388 --> 00:03:21,387
And? What is it?

38
00:03:21,388 --> 00:03:23,287
It's a kudzu drink.

39
00:03:23,288 --> 00:03:26,387
I hear it's good for hangovers too!

40
00:03:26,388 --> 00:03:28,387
I mean you know,

41
00:03:28,388 --> 00:03:30,287
you didn't call me, the great detective all the way out here

42
00:03:30,288 --> 00:03:31,987
to the boondocks of the mountains in Nagano

43
00:03:31,988 --> 00:03:36,087
