44
00:03:36,088 --> 00:03:38,288
Of course, not.

45
00:03:39,988 --> 00:03:42,587
You've got a case, right?

46
00:03:42,588 --> 00:03:43,787
Yeah.

47
00:03:43,788 --> 00:03:46,987
First of all. Take a look at this picture!

48
00:03:46,988 --> 00:03:48,687
What's this?

49
00:03:48,688 --> 00:03:51,187
Human. No, an animal?

50
00:03:51,188 --> 00:03:53,187
