51
00:03:53,188 --> 00:03:54,787
Take a good look!

52
00:03:54,788 --> 00:03:57,587
At the stuff, it's carrying on its back!

53
00:03:57,588 --> 00:04:01,187
It's a sickle, sickle! An animal that has sickles.

54
00:04:01,188 --> 00:04:03,387
A demon that appears riding on whirlwinds

55
00:04:03,388 --> 00:04:06,187
