71
00:04:54,088 --> 00:04:56,587
which makes all kinds of tricks possible.

72
00:04:56,588 --> 00:04:59,787
That picture wasn't tampered with.

73
00:04:59,788 --> 00:05:01,887
That picture was taken with an analog film

74
00:05:01,888 --> 00:05:03,787
that's difficult to tamper with.

75
00:05:03,788 --> 00:05:05,787
And, we had a specialist look at it too,

76
00:05:05,788 --> 00:05:07,987
so there's no mistake about it!

77
00:05:07,988 --> 00:05:11,287
Are you the writer of this picture?

78
00:05:11,288 --> 00:05:14,187
Yes! I'm a writer for the monthly magazine IZUNA,

79
00:05:14,188 --> 00:05:15,987
Daigo Nakama!

80
00:05:15,988 --> 00:05:20,387
I'm here today to take a picture of the Kamaitachi myself.

81
00:05:20,388 --> 00:05:21,487
Oh.

82
00:05:21,488 --> 00:05:23,987
