83
00:05:23,988 --> 00:05:26,687
Is there any connection between Kamaitachi and how cold it is?

84
00:05:26,688 --> 00:05:30,187
Well, there are many Kamaitachi legends

85
00:05:30,188 --> 00:05:32,188
in snowy regions, you see.

86
00:05:32,988 --> 00:05:35,887
