88
00:05:39,788 --> 00:05:41,588
I'm going home!

89
00:05:42,288 --> 00:05:43,687
Don't worry.

90
00:05:43,688 --> 00:05:44,987
Even if such a thing were to appear,

91
00:05:44,988 --> 00:05:49,187
