96
00:05:59,988 --> 00:06:02,387
I'm sure he just came here without a choice

97
00:06:02,388 --> 00:06:04,187
because he got a lot of complaints saying,

98
00:06:04,188 --> 00:06:07,087
"Quit putting on fake pictures", correct?

99
