124
00:07:11,588 --> 00:07:13,787
I was just going to start from now.

125
00:07:13,788 --> 00:07:16,287
Then, hurry up and get with it.

126
00:07:16,288 --> 00:07:17,588
Okay!

127
00:07:18,388 --> 00:07:20,687
Wow! What terribly chapped skin.

128
00:07:20,688 --> 00:07:22,287
Are you all right, Takami?

129
00:07:22,288 --> 00:07:25,387
Yes. Last year, after my husband passed away of an illness,

130
00:07:25,388 --> 00:07:27,687
I've had so many things to do, you see.

131
00:07:27,688 --> 00:07:29,387
What? You know...

132
00:07:29,388 --> 00:07:31,187
Each other?

133
00:07:31,188 --> 00:07:34,087
Yeah! We were classmates in Jr. high school.

134
00:07:34,088 --> 00:07:37,287
I'm sorry, I posted a strange picture on the magazine.

135
00:07:37,288 --> 00:07:38,887
