136
00:07:38,888 --> 00:07:42,487
Nope, in fact we've been getting more guests thanks to it.

137
00:07:42,488 --> 00:07:44,487
Well, because of the Kamaitachi,

138
00:07:44,488 --> 00:07:47,887
