145
00:08:04,588 --> 00:08:08,287
I guess the only way to increase guests would be to use that.

146
00:08:08,288 --> 00:08:10,287
Don't you think so too?

147
00:08:10,288 --> 00:08:13,788
I already refused the other day, didn't I?

148
00:08:15,088 --> 00:08:17,587
Well, once the demon fuss subsides

149
00:08:17,588 --> 00:08:19,587
and you go through tough management again,

150
00:08:19,588 --> 00:08:21,687
I guess you'll change your mind.

151
00:08:21,688 --> 00:08:26,287
If someone were to be killed by that thing called Kamaitachi,

152
00:08:26,288 --> 00:08:28,488
it would be a different story, though.

153
00:08:30,488 --> 00:08:32,788
Nyo... Nyotaimori?

154
00:08:33,388 --> 00:08:35,287
Is he telling you to do that stuff where you place sashimi

155
00:08:35,288 --> 00:08:39,987
on the body of a woman and entertain the guests?

156
00:08:39,988 --> 00:08:42,787
Yes, he says that the guests would double.

157
00:08:42,788 --> 00:08:45,287
I've never seen something like that

158
00:08:45,288 --> 00:08:46,987
except in erotic samurai movies.

159
00:08:46,988 --> 00:08:49,887
If the word gets out, you'd get nabbed for public indecency.

160
00:08:49,888 --> 00:08:52,287
Well, I think he's just joking though.

161
00:08:52,288 --> 00:08:54,687
When I got married and came here,

162
00:08:54,688 --> 00:08:59,387
this inn and my parents' inn merged and was doing well.

163
00:08:59,388 --> 00:09:00,887
But since my husband passed away,

164
00:09:00,888 --> 00:09:02,987
the number of regular guests decreased

165
00:09:02,988 --> 00:09:05,487
