166
00:09:05,488 --> 00:09:09,387
But, Takami, don't ever do Nyotaimori.

167
00:09:09,388 --> 00:09:11,387
Then, why don't you sell something?

168
00:09:11,388 --> 00:09:14,087
Like antique vases.

169
00:09:14,088 --> 00:09:17,087
Come to think of it, there's a large sickle in the storeroom

170
00:09:17,088 --> 00:09:19,987
