176
00:09:36,188 --> 00:09:39,887
You mean it's the one that was in the picture?

177
00:09:39,888 --> 00:09:42,987
The one the Kamaitachi was carrying?

178
00:09:42,988 --> 00:09:45,387
Where is this storeroom?

179
00:09:45,388 --> 00:09:47,187
Near the outdoor bath.

180
00:09:47,188 --> 00:09:48,387
Please take us there then!

181
00:09:48,388 --> 00:09:49,788
Okay!

182
00:09:53,788 --> 00:09:56,588
See? It's starting to get interesting, no?

183
00:09:57,888 --> 00:10:00,487
Give me that audio data file then.

184
00:10:00,488 --> 00:10:02,788
No, not just yet.

185
00:10:03,588 --> 00:10:05,287
Let's go, Conan!

186
00:10:05,288 --> 00:10:06,987
Heiji! Hurry up!

187
00:10:06,988 --> 00:10:08,888
-Oh, yes. -Got it.

188
00:10:10,788 --> 00:10:14,888
I think it was someplace around here.

189
00:10:15,788 --> 00:10:17,888
I don't see it.

190
00:10:20,588 --> 00:10:23,487
Boy, this storeroom sure is dusty.

191
00:10:23,488 --> 00:10:27,487
Hey, smoking in a place like this, you'll cause a fire.

192
00:10:27,488 --> 00:10:29,388
Don't worry.

193
00:10:31,288 --> 00:10:33,687
Shall we all help you find it then?

194
00:10:33,688 --> 00:10:35,487
Yes.

195
00:10:35,488 --> 00:10:37,988
I guess we should.

196
00:10:39,488 --> 00:10:40,888
Crap!

197
00:10:42,088 --> 00:10:43,287
