199
00:10:44,688 --> 00:10:46,688
Wow, really!

200
00:10:48,788 --> 00:10:50,887
But if it snows...

201
00:10:50,888 --> 00:10:53,888
It's supposed to come, right? Kamaitachi.

202
00:10:57,388 --> 00:10:58,987
What's with you guys?

203
00:10:58,988 --> 00:11:01,688
I thought you said you'd be waiting outside.

204
00:11:03,288 --> 00:11:05,787
Isn't this it, Takami?

205
00:11:05,788 --> 00:11:08,387
Yes, that's it! It's this sickle!

206
00:11:08,388 --> 00:11:10,787
It sure is antique alright.

207
00:11:10,788 --> 00:11:12,287
It looks expensive.

208
00:11:12,288 --> 00:11:15,988
My late husband used to say it's probably worth 10 million yen.

209
00:11:17,288 --> 00:11:18,787
What?

210
00:11:18,788 --> 00:11:20,188
The light bulb cracked?

211
00:11:21,688 --> 00:11:22,788
Ouch!

212
00:11:23,488 --> 00:11:24,887
Dad?

213
00:11:24,888 --> 00:11:25,987
Heiji?

214
00:11:25,988 --> 00:11:28,587
I don't know what happened but it got my arm.

215
00:11:28,588 --> 00:11:30,588
I got slashed on the back of my hand.

216
00:11:32,188 --> 00:11:33,687
You're right.

217
00:11:33,688 --> 00:11:35,588
