218
00:11:37,888 --> 00:11:39,287
It's the voice of that woman writer.

219
00:11:39,288 --> 00:11:40,787
Where?

220
00:11:40,788 --> 00:11:42,687
Hey, are you all right?

221
00:11:42,688 --> 00:11:44,788
What happened?

222
00:11:46,788 --> 00:11:48,588
Hey, that wound.

223
00:11:52,388 --> 00:11:53,588
It can't be.

224
00:11:54,788 --> 00:11:56,488
Kamaitachi?

225
00:12:01,304 --> 00:12:03,103
Hey, Kazuha!

226
00:12:03,104 --> 00:12:05,003
Did you call the police?

227
00:12:05,004 --> 00:12:08,703
Yes. They said they'd be right over!

228
00:12:08,704 --> 00:12:10,803
But, I wonder if they'd believe our story

229
00:12:10,804 --> 00:12:13,503
about a Kamaitachi attacking us.

230
00:12:13,504 --> 00:12:15,103
Believe us or not,

231
00:12:15,104 --> 00:12:18,603
three people have already been slashed like this.

232
00:12:18,604 --> 00:12:22,103
Well, I guess it'll be all right because this is Nagano

233
00:12:22,104 --> 00:12:24,003
