234
00:12:24,004 --> 00:12:27,203
I see! Inspector Kansuke Yamato!

235
00:12:27,204 --> 00:12:28,403
That's right!

236
00:12:28,404 --> 00:12:32,103
I'm sure that super smart one-eyed Inspector

237
00:12:32,104 --> 00:12:35,603
will solve this Kamaitachi case in no time at all!

238
00:12:35,604 --> 00:12:37,003
Right!

239
00:12:37,004 --> 00:12:38,803
One-eyed.

240
00:12:38,804 --> 00:12:41,403
Come to think of it, Haibara was saying that.

241
00:12:41,404 --> 00:12:43,803
The number two of the Black Organization,

242
00:12:43,804 --> 00:12:46,003
Rum's characteristic was...

243
00:12:46,004 --> 00:12:51,303
While I was at the Organization, I heard various descriptions of Rum.

244
00:12:51,304 --> 00:12:53,503
A large brawny man,

245
00:12:53,504 --> 00:12:55,803
an effeminate man,

246
00:12:55,804 --> 00:12:57,604
an old man.

247
00:12:58,604 --> 00:13:01,103
He injured his eye in some accident,

248
00:13:01,104 --> 00:13:05,203
and either his left or right eye is an artificial eye.

249
00:13:05,204 --> 00:13:09,103
Inspector Yamato one-eyed and a big guy.

250
00:13:09,104 --> 00:13:12,603
If he lets his hair down loose, he's long-haired.

251
00:13:12,604 --> 00:13:14,603
And since he uses a cane, from a distance,

252
00:13:14,604 --> 00:13:17,603
he could look to be an old man.

253
00:13:17,604 --> 00:13:20,604
Hey. Don't tell me Inspector Yamato is...

254
00:13:23,104 --> 00:13:26,704
The police are here.

255
00:13:30,404 --> 00:13:32,603
I'm Inspector Yamamura from the Gunma Prefectural Police!

256
00:13:32,604 --> 00:13:35,903
I have just arrived here, you see.

257
00:13:35,904 --> 00:13:40,203
This is the Nagano Prefecture, isn't it?

258
00:13:40,204 --> 00:13:43,303
This place is just on the border of Gunma, you see!

259
00:13:43,304 --> 00:13:45,803
So, this is our jurisdiction!

260
00:13:45,804 --> 00:13:49,803
So, Inspector Yamato's not going to come?

261
00:13:49,804 --> 00:13:52,703
I thought we be able to meet Yui too.

262
00:13:52,704 --> 00:13:54,203
Hey.

263
00:13:54,204 --> 00:13:57,203
What's with that disappointed attitude of yours?

264
00:13:57,204 --> 00:13:59,203
The flaming dog case,

